# Personal Expense Tracker (Python CLI App)

This is a simple command-line based expense tracker I built using Python. It allows you to record your daily expenses, view them anytime, and even see a pie chart of your spending by category. All data is saved in a CSV file, so it's lightweight and doesn't need any database setup.

### âœ¨ Features:
- Add new expenses with category, amount, and optional description
- View all past expenses from the CSV
- Automatically generates a pie chart using Matplotlib to show where your money goes
- Data stored locally in `expenses.csv` â€” no internet required

